## If you want to go deeper

Developers on the project will look at folders such as:

- **`src/`** — user interface and browser logic  
- **`api/`** — Vercel function for the optional AI recipe endpoint  
- **`lib/llm/`** — shared parsing and types for structured recipes  
- **`documentation/`** — notes like this one  

That’s enough to orient a curious non-developer to how ScreenToKitchen fits together technically—without needing to read the code line by line.
